# GameNative — Player Profile Screen

## Overview

When a user taps a friend in the friends list, they go to the PlayerProfileScreen
FIRST — not directly to chat. Chat is accessed from a button on the profile screen.

Navigation flow:
```
FriendsListScreen
    └── tap friend
        └── PlayerProfileScreen
            ├── [Message] button → ChatScreen
            ├── [Achievements] tab → ProfileAchievementsTab
            └── [Games] tab → ProfileGamesTab
```

All screens use existing gn_* tokens. No new colors. No new dependencies beyond
what is already in the project (landscapist-coil, Room, SteamKit callbacks).

