## Part 2 — ProfileAchievementsTab.kt

This is the same achievement list from AchievementsScreen but scoped to this
specific friend's steamId. Reuse AchievementRepository with the friend's steamId.

Show exactly the same design as AchievementsScreen:
- Progress header card with circular arc + gradient bar
- Filter chips: All / Unlocked / Locked
- Achievement cards: icon (color if unlocked, grayscale if locked), name,
  description, unlock date, teal checkmark or gray lock icon
- Left teal border on unlocked rows
- Empty state if no data

The only difference from the main AchievementsScreen:
- No "Compare with me" button (user is already on a friend's profile)
- Progress shows THEIR count, not yours

