## Design constraints (same as all other screens)

- Background: gnBgDeepest (#09090F) everywhere
- Cards: gnBgSurface (#12121C), 10-12dp corners, gnBorderCard 1dp stroke, elevation=0
- Fonts: GameNativeFontFamily (Outfit) via PluviaTypography — never system font
- Do NOT define new colors — only existing gn_* tokens from Color.kt
- No elevation shadows — stroke only
- Avatar border color = presence state color (see above)
- Currently playing indicator = pulsing gnNeonTeal dot, never static
- Recent activity accent = gnAccentPrimary/gnAccentGlow
- Unlocked/active accent = gnNeonTeal
- Level/XP accent = gnNeonPurple
- Image loading: landscapist-coil pattern from LibraryAppItem
- Shimmer on all loading states using existing ShimmerFrameLayout pattern
- LazyColumn key = { game.appId } and key = { achievement.apiName }
  (stable keys, same pattern as library list)
- All fetch operations: viewModelScope.launch + Dispatchers.IO for network/db,
  collect on Dispatchers.Main for UI state updates
